{"tid":498867,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"70歲伯伯低頭坐火車 唔係瞓咗係死咗","createTime":"2017-12-14T07:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T07:50:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"de331c1a910345c9c379168fb93b0899295ba8ef","tid":498867,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171213/large/1513137843_9df7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171213%2Flarge%2F1513137843_9df7.jpg&h=0c7f0306&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n墨西哥一班乘客在不知情的情況下伴屍坐火車。一名70歲男子乘火車時心臟病發，由於他低着頭坐在關愛座，火車的乘客誤以為他睡着了而一直沒有為意，直至職員巡查時因無法喚醒他便召救護員到場，始發現他已經死去數小時。<br />\n<br />\n從相片看到，男子頭部挨着欄杆，驟眼看以為他睡着。火車職員至晚上11時45分巡查時，見男子仍坐在座位上，卻無法喚醒他，便召救護員，證實他已經去世數小時。<br />\n<br />\n其後的檢查顯示，男子因突發性心肌炎(fulminant myocarditis)引致心臟衰竭死亡，他的遺體送到殮房後由親人認領。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171214/57575135\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171214%2F57575135&d=y%2Fqd8MyStx9%2BQdFqO2ApWsmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=fe9fb9aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171214%2F57575135&h=c1239219\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171214/57575135</a>"}]}